msg: Adjusted style for H5 (increased font size by 0.1em, compensated by reducing bottom margin and added more whitespace before the heading. Apache documents generated with Texen typically use a lot more small sub headings than is usual. This adds a stronger visual clue that H5 are not H6 headings.
